==French==
===Pronunciation===
*/ʒamɛ/, /ZamE/

===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[iam]] [[magis]]'', yet more.

===Adverb===
'''jamais'''

#[[never]]
#:''Je ne l'ai jamais vue'' - I've never seen her
#[[ever]]
#:''Es-tu jamais allé en France?'' - Did you ever go to France?

====Usage note====
:''Ne'' is used when ''jamais'' means ''never'', but not when it means ''ever''.

